      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a project car or for parts. The exterior has significant body damage, including deep rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. Mechanically, the engine runs but suffers from a persistent oil leak and a slipping transmission that will require immediate attention. It is not currently recommended for long-distance driving in its present state.",
