    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project or a budget-friendly starter car? This vehicle is in poor condition and will need some mechanical and cosmetic TLC, but it\u2019s a fantastic opportunity for a DIY enthusiast to bring it back to life! It\u2019s an honest car with a lot of character, ready for someone who isn't afraid to roll up their sleeves and get to work.",
