      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, this is definitely the one! I\u2019ve kept up with all the maintenance, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 showcases the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering with its S54 3.2L inline-six and six independent throttle bodies. Power is delivered via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This unit features documented VANOS maintenance and proactive subframe reinforcement, ensuring the chassis handles the high-revving output with composure. With its balanced 50/50 weight distribution and communicative hydraulic steering, this driver-focused example offers a raw, mechanical connection to the road. The vehicle presents in well-maintained condition with minor cosmetic wear appropriate for its mileage.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Runs smooth.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
